canWithdraw(bytes32,address).notice: Returns whether a withdrawal can be made

deleteTrust(bytes32).notice: Delete a trust - must have 0 balance

depositTrust(bytes32).notice: Deposit some ETH to this account

getTrustAtIndex(uint256).notice: Read the trust details at a given index (used to iterate)

updateTrust(bytes32,address,address[],st.notice: Update some of the settings of the trust (not all)

validateAddresses(address,address[],addr.notice: Validate address fields for a trust
